An [OpenClaw](https://github.com/openclaw) **Tool** plugin scaffolded with [ClawForge](https://github.com/hidearmoon/clawforge).

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
```

Or add to your OpenClaw `plugins` directory and restart.

## Configuration

Edit `openclaw.plugin.json` to adjust config defaults:

```json
{
  "config": {
    "timeout": 10
  }
}
```

## Development

```bash
# Start hot-reload sandbox
clawforge dev .

# Run tests
pytest
```

## Plugin Interface

| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `init(config)` | Called once after plugin load |
| `run(payload)` | Invoked when the tool is triggered |
| `shutdown()` | Called before plugin unload |

